                                                </p>\
                                            </li>\
                                            <li class="navPage-subMenu-item-child navPages-action-end">\
                                                <a class="navPage-subMenu-action navPages-action" href="{{theme_settings.mega_menu_style1_item-custom-link1}}"><span class="text">\
                                                {{theme_settings.mega_menu_style1_item-custom-linktext1}}</span></a>\
